Parliament, Monday, 27 August 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Sport and Recreation will tomorrow, meet with the South African Rugby Union on financial reports, governance and related matters. Meeting details are as follows: Date: Tuesday, 28 August 2018
	Venue: Committee Room 2, Upper Ground Floor, 90 Plein Street.
	Time: 09h30 ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON SPORT AND RECREATION, MS BEAUTY DLULANE For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer:
